quran[9{c,v,t}:
25,3,"logon ne ussay chore kar aisay mabood bana liye jo kisi cheez ko peda nahi karte balkay khud peda kiye jatay hain, jo khud apne liye bhi kisi naffa ya nuqsaan ka ikhtiyar nahi rakhtay, jo nah maar satke hain nah jِla satke hain, nah marey hue ko phir utha satke hain"
25,4,jin logon ne NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki baat maan-ne se inkaar kar diya hai woh kehte hain ke yeh Farqan aik mann gharat cheez hai jisay iss shakhs ne aap hi ghurr liya hai aur kuch dosray logon ne iss kaam mein is ki madad ki hai bara zulm aur sakht jhoot hai jis par yeh log utar aeye hain
25,5,kehte hain yeh puranay logon ki likhi hui cheeze hain jinhein yeh shakhs naqal karta hai aur woh isay subah o shaam sunai jati hain
25,6,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho ke"" isay nazil kya hai uss ne jo zameen aur asmano ka bhaid jaanta hai"" haqeeqat yeh hai ke woh bara ghafoor Raheem hai"
25,7,"kehte hain"" yeh kaisa rasool hai jo khana khata hai aur baazaaron mein chalta phirta hai? kyun nah is ke paas koi farishta bheja gaya jo is ke sath rehta aur ( nah maan-ne walon ko ) dhmkata ?"
25,8,"ya aur kuch nahi to iss ke liye koi khazana hi utaar diya jata, ya is ke paas koi baagh hi hota jis se yeh ( itminan ki ) rozi haasil karta"" aur zalim kehte hain"" tum log to aik sehar zada aadmi ke peechay lag gay ho """
25,9,"dekho, kaisi kaisi ajeeb hujjtein yeh log tumahray agay paish kar rahay hain, aisay behke hain ke koi thikaane ki baat inn ko nahi sojhti"
25,10,"bara babarkat hai woh jo agar chahay to un ki tajweez kardah cheezon se bhi ziyada barh charh kar tum ko day sakta hai, ( aik nahi ) bohat se baagh jin ke neechay nehrein behti hon, aur barray barray mehal"
25,11,"asal baat yeh hai ke yeh log"" uss gharri"" ko jhutla chuke hain aur jo uss gharri kojhutla-ay is ke liye hum ne bharakti hui aag muhayya kar rakhi hai"
